PrecisRe-appointment of certain persons as members of the Oil and Gas Committee, established by Order in Council P.C. 1973-265 of February 1, 1973, to hold office for a term of three years, and to designate Edward (Ted) W. Best as chairman of the Oil and Gas Committee for a term of three years, effective July 27, 1992. (Edward (Ted) W. Best, Calgary, Alberta; Laura Jean Nelson, Yellowknife, Northwest Territories; Steven Malcolm Millan, St. John's, Newfoundland; Jacques Farmer, Montreal, Quebec; and John Boyd, Calgary, Alberta)
